SKANDHAN M U - RESUME PLACEHOLDER
================================================================================

This file is a placeholder for your actual professional resume. 

To activate the resume download feature on your portfolio website:
1. Generate your resume as a PDF file (e.g., from Word, Canva, or LaTeX).
2. Rename your PDF file to "resume.pdf".
3. Replace this placeholder file (at c:\portfolio\resume.pdf) with your new file.

Your interactive website modal preview is fully independent and will continue to 
render your details dynamically using modern browser elements!
